  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV86">
<l>cāṭucāṭu pātaṉēca laṅkalanta poykaivā</l>
<l>yāṭarāviṉ vaṉpiṭarna ṭampayiṉṟa nātaṉē</l>
<l>kōṭunīṭu kaiyaceyya pātanāḷu muḷḷiṉāl</l>
<l>vīṭaṉāka meyceyāta vaṇṇameṉkol kaṇṇaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You with the foot that kicked the cart! O Lord who danced</l>
<l>On the mighty hood of the snake that danced in the treacherous pond!</l>
<l>O You with a hand in which the conch thrives! If one meditates upon</l>
<l>[Your] red feet at all times, why do [You] not truly liberate [them]? O Kṛṣṇa!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
